title: IAA Tonight | Former NFL DE John Abraham Joins the Show!
description: Former NFL DE and should be Hall of Famer John Abraham joins the show to talk about his career and HoF resume, life after football dealing with concussions, how defensive lineman are finally getting the respect they deserve, and what's next for him in life.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, LeSean McCoy, John Abraham, Brandon Flowers)
